Package ui.drawing.colour

Class WrappingColouredString

  • java.lang.Object
    • ui.drawing.DrawableSection
      • ui.drawing.DrawableBufferedSection
        • ui.drawing.colour.WrappingColouredString
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BufferedSection, ColouredElement, ResponsiveSection, PrintHandler, Section
    public class WrappingColouredString
extends DrawableBufferedSection
implements ColouredElement, ResponsiveSection
    Renders a coloured string to a fixed size buffer, wrapping at the end of each row.
    A buffered section implementation.
    Represents a section that can be drawn to the terminal window.

      • populateBuffer

        private void populateBuffer()
        Fits the coloured string inside the buffer. If in the middle of a word wrap with a '-', otherwise just break on the space. If max size exceeded truncate.
